name: MISERY
description:
When the twilight comes
I feel half of me is missing
Like innocent
You destroy the feeling that I have planted
When everything is gone
Your shadow is filling again
I don't know what you want
I no longer have the right to bring it up again
Erase the ink you once painted on the canvas of my heart
Tearing all the shadows that appear in the recesses of my soul
Ego has incited me
'To come back to you
But logic says
It's good I stay away
